        <h3>Indexation Allowance for companies</h3>
        <p> If you're a company, you pay tax on your gains as Corporation Tax. 
          You're still entitled to the Indexation Allowance. It's available on 
          all sales or disposals and applies for the whole period of ownership 
          up to and including the month in which you dispose of the asset. Indexation 
          Allowance for companies did not cease in April 2008.</p>
        <p><a href="/rates/cg-indexation-allowance/index.htm"> Go to the Indexation Allowance 
          tables for chargeable gains paid by companies</a></p>
        <p class="gotoTop"><a href="#top" target="_top">Top</a></p>
